name: SaintCrypto #08
description:
The beginning of the crypto era and the birth of the Metaverse encourages the formation of its own epic, a new mythology.  New myths - new gods, spirits, saints, inspirers and patrons of man will come to the Metaverse to become part of it.
My Saints Crypto are created from nature itself with the help of digital technologies and artificial intelligence.  Their stylistic similarity with the masks of African tribes refers us to the history of proto-humanity, which emerged from the African continent 200 thousand years ago.  As an artist, this thought inspires me, pushes me to draw unifying lines from the distant past to the future.
The Pantheon of the Saints of Crypto is open to contemplation and acquisition.
